snippet.textDisplay: I couldn't put my finger on why this kind of intimacy between a daughter and father is uncomfortable for me, yet it's beautiful and I love seeing it. Then I realized my own father was sexually inappropriate with me and my sister. I always felt I had to hide my beauty from my dad. Like I couldn't be my most beautiful self in fear that he would be attracted to me inappropriately. Seeing her sing so sweetly and look him in the eyes this way is pure and beautiful. I now understand as a little girl how I hid this part of my soul. It's healing to watch this relationship as an example of how a father can look at his daughter with pure eyes and no bad intentions.
